In response to Bill's goading on the MT/V5 issue, I have actually
firmed up a little on the V5 side of the argument. Here's the
reasoning as I expressed it to Bill:

>From Bill:
> And by the way,
> did you tell Brian he should use "V5" instead of "MT"?  Why in
